Deflate the tarball by typing

  tar xzf fragrep-2.tar.gz

Then, type 

  cd fragrep2
  make release

in the directory containing all fragrep files. Refer to the
manpage (fragrep.1) for
further instructions.

To make the man page available via the man command, copy fragrep.1 to

  /usr/local/man/man1

or any other directory contained in your $MANPATH directory.

fragrep has been implemented in C++ using gcc Version 4.0.1. 


